\viewkind4\uc1\pard\nowidctlpar\cf1\lang1033\b\f0\fs16 TRzPageControl & TRzTabControl\b0\par
\cf0\f1 The \b TRzPageControl \b0 and \b TRzTabControl \b0 components are native VCL implementations of a PageControl and TabControl, respectively. That is, neither control requires the Windows Common Controls library. However, these custom controls offer many more display options than the common control versions. \par
\par
In particular, there are four styles of tabs to choose from by using the \b TabStyle \b0 property. Plus, there are options to change the colors of the tabs using the \b TabColors \b0 and \b UseColoredTabs \b0 properties. Tab text is controlled by the \b TextAlignment\b0 , \b TextAlignmentVertical\b0 , \b TextColors\b0 , and \b TextOrientation \b0 properties. Images from an image list can be displayed on tabs using the \b Images\b0 , \b ImageAlignment\b0 , \b ImageAlignmentVertical\b0 , \b ImageMargin\b0 , and \b ImagePosition \b0 properties.\par
